Titolo: Brothers in Arms: Double Time

Anno: 2008

Descrizione: Brothers in Arms: Double Time is a first-person shooter video game compilation for the Wii and OS X platforms. The title is a compilation of the first two Brothers in Arms games, Brothers in Arms: Road to Hill 30 and Brothers in Arms: Earned in Blood and was developed by Gearbox Software and published by Ubisoft. It features 31 levels set during the Battle of Normandy.
The Wii version of the game uses the motion sensing abilities of the Wiimote and the Nunchuk attachment for issuing battle gestures and squad commands during gameplay. It lacks any multiplayer features.
The OS X version of Brothers in Arms: Double Time was released on April 16, 2010 by Feral Interactive.

Genere: First-person shooter

Valutazione: N/A
